title: Science Parks fonts ID
content:
Dear Typophiles!

Pretty please...

ID the typefaces used in VIDEUM Science Park.

[http://rforetagen.se/Kronobergs\_l%C3%A4n/V%C3%A4xj%C3%B6/Videum\_Science\_...](http://web.archive.org/web/20100202145036/http:/rforetagen.se/Kronobergs_l%C3%A4n/V%C3%A4xj%C3%B6/Videum_Science_Park_V%C3%A4xj%C3%B6/ "http://rforetagen.se/Kronobergs\_l%C3%A4n/V%C3%A4xj%C3%B6/Videum\_Science\_Park\_V%C3%A4xj%C3%B6/")

And, when possible (the quality is quite terrible), KRINOVA Scienca Park.

[http://www.krinova.se/](http://web.archive.org/web/20100202145036/http:/www.krinova.se/ "http://www.krinova.se/")

Thanks in advance!  
Rafal
author: Rafal Szczawinski

comments.content:
Videum Science Park could be a customized Adobe Insignia?

--- Tamas Ferencz ---

Thank you, Tamas!

It is, indeed, Insignia. It's not even modified, they just used alternates provided in the font.

You have been most helpful.

Best regards,  
Rafal
